Loss Averse StrategiesPVG Loss Averse Strategies are designed to try and prevent major market losses in your portfolio. We are proactively hedging against market risk and attempting to capture value in our security selection.

Loss Averse Equity Income
High Income
Core Equity

  Tactical StrategiesPVG Tactical Strategies are designed to try and capture market participation as well as minimize losses in your portfolio. We are proactively hedging against market risk and attempting to capture value in our security selection. Some strategies are utilizing algorithm based models as well.

Dynamic Core
